XP and Leveling System:
Function AddXP(amount: number, source: "bug_fixed" | "eco_tip_applied"):
  user.xp += amount
  UpdateSidePanelXPBar()

  // Level-up logic
  xp_required = 100 * user.level
  If user.xp >= xp_required:
    user.level += 1
    ShowCelebrationModal("Level Up! ðŸŽ‰ Now Level " + user.level)
    SaveUserData()

  // Track stats for achievements
  If source == "bug_fixed":
    user.bugs_fixed += 1
  Else if source == "eco_tip_applied":
    user.eco_tips_applied += 1
